rComments: One of the best profs I've had so far. He was clear in his lectures and made evolution interesting! The concepts were explained properly as he has a passion for the subject and if you take notes and actually study, it's easy to get a good mark in his class. Side note: he's a bee guy.

It was his first time teaching this course and he didn't do well, he tried to cram content and ended up missing out on a lot of major details. Make sure to read the textbook and take notes, and get ready for very long application and thinking questions on the module test.
